# Interview Tips

* The final linked list follows **Preorder Traversal**.
* Never lose the original right subtree.
* Always attach the original right subtree to the **rightmost node** of the left subtree.
* After rearranging, move to `current.right`.

---

# One-Line Memory Trick ⭐

> **Find the rightmost node of the left subtree → Attach the original right subtree → Move the left subtree to the right → Set `left = null` → Move to the next node.**
